This subject of Huns add additional functions (info of time staple iostat and vmstat )
1. make sure execute it by root.
2. create a folder var/log/Huns
3. because this project use "execl" to implement a child process, since exec need a full path of file which gonna to be 
   invoked,so please place the file in the appropiatlly. In this case, iostat and vmstat are suppose to be at 
   /home/vpathak/Documents/program/  .
4. compile the save_resume_log and run the generated file.